<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Терминал вакансий | NULLPTR</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center px-5 py-3 brutal-border-bottom bg-transparent">
        <a class="brand-font fs-3 text-uppercase fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none" href="/">
            { NULL<span class="text-accent">PTR</span> }
        </a>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-4">
            <a href="#" class="brand-font fw-bold text-uppercase text-dark text-decoration-none">Все вакансии</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn rounded-0 brutal-border brutal-shadow fw-bold text-uppercase brand-font text-dark">Для компаний</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="px-5 py-4 brutal-border-bottom">
        <h1 class="display-4 brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold mb-0">Терминал вакансий</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="d-flex">
        
        <aside class="p-5 brutal-border-end" style="width: 350px; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <div class="position-sticky" style="top: 2rem;">
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control rounded-0 brutal-border bg-transparent p-3 brand-font mb-3" placeholder="Поиск по стеку или должности...">
                    <button class="btn btn-dark rounded-0 brutal-border brutal-shadow w-100 fw-bold text-uppercase brand-font py-3">Искать</button>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold brutal-border-bottom pb-2 mb-4">Грейд</h4>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <input class="form-check-input brutal-checkbox m-0" type="checkbox" id="mid">
                        <label class="fw-bold mt-1" for="mid">Middle</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <input class="form-check-input brutal-checkbox m-0" type="checkbox" id="sen" checked>
                        <label class="fw-bold mt-1" for="sen">Senior</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <input class="form-check-input brutal-checkbox m-0" type="checkbox" id="lead">
                        <label class="fw-bold mt-1" for="lead">Lead</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold brutal-border-bottom pb-2 mb-4">Формат</h4>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <input class="form-check-input brutal-checkbox m-0" type="checkbox" id="rem" checked>
                        <label class="fw-bold mt-1" for="rem">Remote</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <input class="form-check-input brutal-checkbox m-0" type="checkbox" id="off">
                        <label class="fw-bold mt-1" for="off">Office</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="p-5 flex-grow-1">
            
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-5">
                <span class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold fs-5">Найдено: 3</span>
                <select class="form-select rounded-0 brutal-border bg-transparent brand-font fw-bold w-auto cursor-pointer">
                    <option selected>Новые сверху</option>
                    <option value="1">Зарплата: по убыванию</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="card rounded-0 brutal-border brutal-shadow mb-4 p-4 bg-white">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="h4 brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold mb-2">Senior Frontend Engineer</h3>
                        <div class="fw-bold mb-3">
                            <span class="text-dark">FinTech Core</span> &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Москва / Remote</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">React</span>
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">TypeScript</span>
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">FSD</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-end border-start border-2 border-dark ps-4">
                        <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-uppercase text-accent mb-3">350K - 450K ₽</div>
                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-0 brutal-border fw-bold text-uppercase brand-font text-dark btn-sm px-4">Детали</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card rounded-0 brutal-border brutal-shadow mb-4 p-4 bg-white">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="h4 brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold mb-2">Go Backend Developer</h3>
                        <div class="fw-bold mb-3">
                            <span class="text-dark">StreamData</span> &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Remote</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">Golang</span>
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">PostgreSQL</span>
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">Kafka</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-end border-start border-2 border-dark ps-4">
                        <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-uppercase text-accent mb-3">€4000 - €6000</div>
                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-0 brutal-border fw-bold text-uppercase brand-font text-dark btn-sm px-4">Детали</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card rounded-0 brutal-border brutal-shadow mb-4 p-4 bg-white">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="h4 brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold mb-2">Lead DevOps / SRE</h3>
                        <div class="fw-bold mb-3">
                            <span class="text-dark">CloudNexus</span> &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Санкт-Петербург / Office</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">Terraform</span>
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">Ansible</span>
                            <span class="badge border border-dark text-dark rounded-0 px-2 py-1 text-uppercase">AWS</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-end border-start border-2 border-dark ps-4">
                        <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-uppercase text-accent mb-3">От 400 000 ₽</div>
                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-0 brutal-border fw-bold text-uppercase brand-font text-dark btn-sm px-4">Детали</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-5 border-top border-dark border-2 bg-white mt-auto">
        <div>
            <h4 class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold mb-2">NULLPTR JOB BOARD</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">Строгий отбор. Никаких скрытых условий. Только инженерия и хардкор.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex gap-4">
            <a href="#" class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none">About</a>
            <a href="#" class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none">Telegram</a>
            <a href="#" class="brand-font text-uppercase fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none">Github</a>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>